            {
                "title": "Discussion",
                "body": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "body": "Physics can manifest in multiple ways in games, but when it is a focus element of the game it is usually part of riddles or puzzles that need to be solved by understanding the game physics. This can for example be in form of stacking objects or managing bodies of water. This tag should not be used to identify games that generally apply phsics to their gameobject, since this does not require the player to interact with said physics."
                    }
